VERDICT: VARIANCE  --  same post-entry-reversal / chop-gate-blind-spot pattern as
btc h20. The chop gate DID engage on SOL (per-coin SOLUSDT spot present 100% in the
trader's authoritative DB). All 4 losses were directional moves that cleared the gate
then reversed by settle. SOL-specific bad hour (BTC/ETH both green same hour); 6/10
vs 83% all-time is binomial p=0.073 -- unusual but inside normal variance. KEEP THE GATE.

